<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">










</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<div class="WoedContainer Writing">
<div class="skips">
<div class="labels">
<div class="title" data-heading="A Tasteful Collection">A Tasteful Collection</div>
</div>
<div id="u-scps-block"><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑2105 || Programmable Occult</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑2105 || Programmable Occult</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Revenge? Self‑improvement? Worship? It's all a few key presses away&#8230; but is it worth the cost?</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2105">SCP-2105</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1414893826 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Nov 2014 02:03</span></li>
<li>(+170)</li>
<li><em>&quot;When Response Team M82 responded to the alarm, they found Dr. Forsyth and Dr. Marberry cleanly dismembered with no signs of struggle.&quot;</em></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4378 || Her Noodly Appendage</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4378 || Her Noodly Appendage</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li><em>Cogito, ergo sum pasta.</em> Don't touch that lasagna.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4378">SCP-4378</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1544811144 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">14 Dec 2018 18:12</span></li>
<li>(+102)</li>
<li><em>&quot;A single piece of spaghetti found at the bottom of President █████ ███████'s bowl arranged in cursive writing spelling out &quot;hello?&quot;&quot;</em></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4205 || In⁠ ⁠The⁠ ⁠Eyes of⁠ ⁠the⁠ ⁠Beholder</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4205 || In⁠ ⁠The⁠ ⁠Eyes of⁠ ⁠the⁠ ⁠Beholder⁠ ⁠⧲•⧲</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>“If you remember me, then I don't care if everyone else forgets.” ― <em>Haruki Murakami, Kafka on the Shore</em></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4205">SCP-4205</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1547244876 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Jan 2019 22:14</span></li>
<li>(+1504)</li>
<li>&quot;Why did I never tell him?<br />
<br />
<em>Why did I never tell myself?</em>&quot;</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Tale || COMPWAN Source Manipulator</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Tale || COMPWAN Source Manipulator</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>There's probably easier ways to get rid of someone you don't like&#8230;</li>
<li><a href="/compwan-source-manipulator">COMPWAN Source Manipulator</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1547834100 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 Jan 2019 17:55</span></li>
<li>(+34)</li>
<li><strong><tt>A program to compile the imperfect flesh.</tt></strong></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4512 || A&nbsp;Goddamn Filthy&nbsp;Teleporting Party&nbsp;Pool</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4512 || A&nbsp;Goddamn Filthy&nbsp;Teleporting Party&nbsp;Pool</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>This bad boy is a big, mean, luau party machine!</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4512">SCP-4512</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1550764470 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Feb 2019 15:54</span></li>
<li>(+138)</li>
<li>SCP-4512 is a 40 square meter sapient swimming pool capable of instantaneous translocation.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Tale || The Moon's Stellar Companion</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Tale || The Moon's Stellar Companion</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Fun, exciting, magnificent Buddhist space adventure!</li>
<li><a href="/the-moons-stellar-companion">The Moon's Stellar Companion</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1554473508 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">05 Apr 2019 14:11</span></li>
<li>(+42)</li>
<li>Gold columns rise above me endlessly, though I can see the very top as beings with hundreds of arms dance upon them to a silent rhythm.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4522 || The ⁠Mystical ⁠Village of ⁠the ⁠Jade ⁠Peach</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4522 || The ⁠Mystical ⁠Village of ⁠the ⁠Jade ⁠Peach</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>“Losing the possibility of something is the exact same thing as losing hope and without hope nothing can survive.” ― <em>Mark Z. Danielewski, House of Leaves</em></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4522">SCP-4522</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1555600383 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 Apr 2019 15:13</span></li>
<li>(+70)</li>
<li>Forgiveness is not something you beg or ask for, intruder.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4485 || Such Black Light</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4485 || Such Black Light</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>“As I sat on the chair I pondered sadly, but not desperately, Why the core of the world exuded such black light.” ― <em>Jean Hans Arp</em></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4485">SCP-4485</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1567001013 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 Aug 2019 14:03</span></li>
<li>(+255)</li>
<li>understanding is searching for an empty cup from which to drink air</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4801 || Ceto‑vimutti: Deliverance&nbsp;From&nbsp;Suffering</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP‑4801 || Ceto‑vimutti: Deliverance&nbsp;From&nbsp;Suffering</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>“This noble truth of suffering has been fully understood': thus, bhikkhus, in regard to things unheard before, there arose in me vision &#8230; and light. ” ― <em>The Blessed One</em></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4801">SCP-4801</a></li>
<li><span class="odate time_1576175546 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">12 Dec 2019 18:32</span></li>
<li>(+49)</li>
<li>Stripped bare, torn, sheared, and destroyed. And so now we can find a form far more refined. We have arrived.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">About Me</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Oh geez, why did you click this?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Hello! It somewhat befuddles me that anyone would click this. But if you truly want to know more about me, this is the place! Too bad I am absolutely awful at writing about myself. But still, I'll give some things&#8230;<br />
<br />
I am a graphic designer for a living. I've made art and wrote for as long as I can remember.<br />
<br />
I'm also gay and a dude, if that's something you care about. Came out really late in life, so that factors in to my writing quite a bit.<br />
<br />
I really like writing stories that have mysteries to unpack. Like puzzles for the reader to find. I try to leave in little clues rather than just outright telling people.<br />
<br />
Okay, that's all you get. Thanks for stopping by!</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
